        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/condi-virtuoso/">&lt;p&gt;A primarily bleed based build that applies bleed through critical hits.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;notes&quot;&gt;Notes&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Condition  Virtuoso is a build that is simple to play and provides very consistent damage with high range. That allows you to freely position yourself and maintain your damage output, even when mechanics force you into range.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This build is also capable of doing large amounts of CC, and has multiple skills that can be swapped around for more utility, making it an excellent build for almost all bosses and situations.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is also relatively sturdy for a DPS build, and has good HP self sustain.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;gearing&quot;&gt;Gearing&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt; &lt;em&gt;There are multiple gear combinations that will arrive at the same total value of stats.&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; &lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
